title: Jazz - Louis Armstrong 1924-58
description:
Jazz - Louis Armstrong 1924-58

There is a lot here to download.
Each of folders 06 thru 13 has at least 20 tracks.
In all, there are over 400 tracks. 

That is all I will do for at least a month because I am leaving for Europe.

Let me mention some useful points.  
You can download any part of the torrent 
And do another part later.  
Click Select None 
and then select only the tracks you want at the time.
And Let Them Seed until you want to go for more.

Folders 00 thru 05 plus the documents is one CDs worth.
Folders 07 thru 13 is one CDs worth.
Folder 06 plus 14 thru 20 is one CDs worth.

You can go for even less at a time.
Then let it keep seeding until you are ready for more.

What I have just explained is part of the advantage
of having large torrents with many Folders.
That is, you can choose 
while you are helping to support a bigger choice.
